quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  25,12,jis waqt woh un ko daur se dekhe gi ( to ghazabnak ho rahi hogi aur yeh ) is ke josh ( ghazab ) aur cheekhnay chalanay ko sunen ge
  25,13,aur jab yeh dozakh ki kisi tang jagah mein ( zanjeeroon mein ) jakar kar daaley jayen ge to wahan mout ko pukaarain ge
  25,14,aaj aik hi mout ko nah poukaro bohat si mouton ko poukaro
  25,15,pucho ke yeh behtar hai ya bahisht javedani jis ka parhaiz garon se wada hai. yeh un ( ke amlon ) ka badla aur rehne ka thikana hoga
  25,16,wahan jo chahain ge un ke liye muyassar hoga hamesha is mein rahen ge. yeh wada khuda ko ( poora karna ) lazim hai aur is Laiq hai ke maang liya jaye
  25,17,aur jis din ( khuda ) un ko aur unn ko jinhein yeh khuda ke siwa pujte hain jama kere ga to farmaiye gakiya tum ne mere un bundon ko gumraahkiya tha ya yeh khud gumraah hogaye they
  25,18,woh kahin ge to pak hai hamein yeh baat Shayan nah thi ke tairay siwa ouron ko dost banatay. lekin to ne hi un ko aur un ke baap dada ko baratnay ko naematain den yahan taq ke woh teri yaad ko bhool gay. aur yeh halaak honay walay log they
  25,19,to ( kafroo ) unhon ne to tum ko tumhari baat mein jhutla diya. pas ( ab ) tum ( azaab ko ) nah phair satke ho. nah ( kisi se ) madad le satke ho. aur jo shakhs tum mein se zulm kere ga hum is ko barray azaab ka maza chkhayin ge
  25,20,aur hum ne tum se pehlay jitne paighambar beje hain sab khana khatay they aur baazaaron mein chaltay phirtay they. aur hum ne tumhe aik dosray ke liye azmaish banaya hai.kiya tum sabr karo ge. aur tumhara perwar-digaar to dekhnay wala hai
